{
  "stem": "18102.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 72.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Good morning, hello.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Good to see you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, of course I was born in Bialystok, Poland.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, my earliest memories are what a kid would remember growing up in a rather big town for Poland, but a small town in terms of the world today.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My parents were Yiddish schoolteachers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was not yet-- in my earliest memories, I was not yet of school age.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And while I recognized the fact that Jews were more or less persecuted, my life really didn't get impacted that way as a child.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I knew that every now and then, someone would shout a profanity that-- [POLISH] in Polish.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I really didn't get involved, as a child anyway.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so my life was very, very normal, of course, until September 1, 1939.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Actually, a little before that in preparation for World War II.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Our house was a hub of intellectual activity, because my parents were leaders in various movements within the Jewish society.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so clearly, I do remember people coming to the house, sitting around the table, drinking tea, and discussing world events and the-- what was obviously coming was a big, black cloud that would be World War II.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were concerns.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I recall from my own memory that when my father would talk to me about an impending war, I would visualize it as I did as a child, with warriors sword fighting in the streets.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But that's all I could imagine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't know about airplanes, and bombs, and things like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and the warriors, I always thought, would be in the main streets.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They wouldn't come in our little street where we lived.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But that was the only way I visualized it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And yes, I was conscious that something was afoot.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
